# INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.failure

**Case**

Your intent handler is unable to handle the intent.

## Declaration

```swift
case failure
```

## Reporting a Problem

- **INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.failureRequiringAppLaunch**: The user needs to launch your app to update their focus status.
- **INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.unspecified**: An unspecified response code.
